Timecrimes;;79;;89;;R;;Nacho Vigalondo's time-travel thriller opens with Hector spying on a beautiful woman undressing in the woods near his property. Investigating, he finds her assaulted and he in turn is attacked by a man whose head is swathed in bandages. Fleeing, Hector encounters a scientific facility where a scientist persuades him to hide in a time machine. Traveling back in time just a few hours, he observes himself.;;Mystery & thriller,Adventure,Sci-fi,Action,Drama;;Nacho Vigalondo;;2007;;Karra Elejalde,Candela Fernández,Bárbara Goenaga,Juan Inciarte,Nacho Vigalondo,Libby Brien,Nicole Dionne,Philip Hersh;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/time_crimes